Summary: 
 * Merge from BuildSystem--devel--0.4 branch
 - @jfsuggar.m4 added ACJF_M4_NULL macro which does nothing and discards all its arguments.
 - @libboost.m4: renamed some internal variables to contain boost to prevent
   potential override of these variables by other parts of the BuildSystem.
 - @libsystemoc.m4: Total overhaul of ACJF_CHECK_LIB_SYSTEMOC to use new
   reworked pkgcheck.m4 infrastructure.
 - Improve pkgcheck.m4
   allow recursive calls into ACJF_CHECK_LIB_TESTER
   call <test macro> even if library is from source tree
 - @libsystemoc.m4: Adapt to reworked pkgcheck.m4 infrastructure.
 - @libsgxutils.m4: Bugfix had two bugs inverse logic and detection bug which
   canceled each other out.

